title: #92Noon Friday Football Feast!
description: We replay audio from new Asst HC/Offensive Advisor Gary Kubiak's presser yesterday, our beloved Jamie Hersch joins after being in attendance at MSG for Wild/Rangers last night, Kevin Lynch is in studio as Wolves are back at it tonight and Vikings OC Kevin Stefanski chats with PA to end the show!
